description:
Gremlin Trouble is a light-hearted techno-fantasy adventure comic featuring Gremlins, an obscure but mis-represented type of fairy which specialize in machines and technology. The main character is Cypher, a stormfairy who is deprived of her wings and is turned into a gremlin by an evil spirit. The stories follow her adventures in a future dystopian world where humans live in population centers, completely dependent on their fragile technology to stay alive.

General Information

Trade paperbacks collecting Gremlin Trouble. Each trade contains 6 issues.
name: Gremlin Trouble

description:
STRONGER THAN FICTION is a Science Fiction Comedy set in a strange, sexual, and violent world. The characters are crass, and the plot holes littered throughout are so big, only the inflated boobs of the female cast can fill them.

STRONGER THAN FICTION is an up-its-own-arse examination of the modern adult comic book narrative. Beneath its jagged surface lies a thought-provoking journey through the authors favorite elements and conventions of edgy comic book storytelling.

STRONGER THAN FICTION is both of these things. All you have to do is read it, and decide for yourself which one you want it to be. Me? I go with the boobs every time
name: Stronger Than Fiction
